#: ../../source/language/javascript/deserialization.rst:2
msgid "反序列化"
msgstr "Deserialization"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/deserialization.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/deserialization.rst:6
msgid ""
"JavaScript本身并没有反序列化的实现，但是一些库如node-serialize、serialize-to-"
"js等支持了反序列化功能。这些库通常使用JSON形式来存储数据，但是和原生函数JSON.parse、 "
"JSON.stringify不同，这些库支持任何对象的反序列化，特别是函数，如果使用不当，则可能会出现反序列化问题。"
msgstr "JavaScript itself does not provide a deserialization implementation, but some libraries, such as node-serialize and serialize-to-js, support deserialization. These libraries usually store data in JSON form, but unlike the native JSON.parse and JSON.stringify functions, they support deserialization of arbitrary objects, especially functions. If they are used improperly, deserialization issues may occur."

